{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Animation.ready","mdn_url":"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/ready","locale":"es","native":"Español","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web_Animations_API\">Web Animations API <small>(en-US)</small></a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation\"><code>Animation</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Constructor</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/Animation\"><code>Animation()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Propiedades</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/currentTime\"><code>currentTime</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/effect\"><code>effect</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/finished\"><code>finished</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/id\"><code>id</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/pending\"><code>pending</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/playbackRate\"><code>playbackRate</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/playState\"><code>playState</code></a></li><li><em><code>ready</code></em></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/replaceState\"><code>replaceState</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/startTime\"><code>startTime</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/timeline\"><code>timeline</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Métodos</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/cancel\"><code>cancel()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/commitStyles\"><code>commitStyles()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/finish\"><code>finish()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/pause\"><code>pause()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/persist\"><code>persist()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/play\"><code>play()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/reverse\"><code>reverse()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/updatePlaybackRate\"><code>updatePlaybackRate()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Eventos</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/cancel_event\"><code>cancel</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/finish_event\"><code>finish</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/remove_event\"><code>remove</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Herencia</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Páginas relacionadas a Web Animations</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AnimationEffect\"><code>AnimationEffect</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/AnimationEvent\"><code>AnimationEvent</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AnimationPlaybackEvent\"><code>AnimationPlaybackEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AnimationTimeline\"><code>AnimationTimeline</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/getAnimations\"><code>Document.getAnimations()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/timeline\"><code>Document.timeline</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DocumentTimeline\"><code>DocumentTimeline</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Element/animate\"><code>Element.animate()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/KeyframeEffect\"><code>KeyframeEffect</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>La propiedad de solo-lectura <code>Animation.ready</code> de la <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web_Animations_API\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Web Animations API (en-US)</a> devuelve un <a href=\"/es/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Promise\"><code>Promise</code></a> que se resuelve cuando la animación está lista para reproducirse. Una nueva 'promesa' es creada cada vez que la animación entra en <a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/playState\">play state(estado de reproducción)</a> <code>\"pending\"(pendiente)</code> así como si la reproducción es cancelada, ya que en ambos escenarios, la animación estará lista para ser reiniciada.</p>\n<div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect1\">\n  <p><strong>Nota:</strong> Dado que la misma <a href=\"/es/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Promise\"><code>Promise</code></a> es usada para las solicitudes pendientes de <code>play</code> y<code>pause</code> , se recomienda a los autores que comprueben el estado de la animación cuando se resuelva la promesa.</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"sintaxis","title":"Sintaxis","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> readyPromise <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> Animation<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>ready<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"valor","title":"Valor","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Un <a href=\"/es/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Promise\"><code>Promise</code></a> que se resuelve cuando la animación esta lista para reproducirse. Por lo general, se usará una construcción similar a esta usando una promise lista:</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>animation<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>ready<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">then</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// Hace lo que sea necesario cuando</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// la animación está lista para reproducirse</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"ejemplo","title":"Ejemplo","isH3":false,"content":"<p>En el siguiente ejemplo, el estado de la animación será <code>running(reproduciendo)</code> cuando la <strong>Promise actual</strong> se resuelva ya que la animación no deja el estado de reproducción <code>pending</code> entre las llamadas <code>pause</code> and <code>play</code> ,por lo tanto, la <strong>Promise actual</strong> no cambia.</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>animation<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">pause</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nanimation<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>ready<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">then</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// Displays 'running'</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">alert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>animation<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>playState<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nanimation<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">play</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"Especificaciones","id":"especificaciones","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://drafts.csswg.org/web-animations-1/#dom-animation-ready","title":"Web Animations"}],"query":"api.Animation.ready"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Compatibilidad con navegadores","id":"compatibilidad_con_navegadores","isH3":false,"query":"api.Animation.ready","dataURL":"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/ready/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"ver_también","title":"Ver también","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web_Animations_API\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Web Animations API (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation\"><code>Animation</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/playState\"><code>Animation.playState</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Sintaxis","id":"sintaxis"},{"text":"Ejemplo","id":"ejemplo"},{"text":"Especificaciones","id":"especificaciones"},{"text":"Compatibilidad con navegadores","id":"compatibilidad_con_navegadores"},{"text":"Ver también","id":"ver_también"}],"summary":"La propiedad de solo-lectura Animation.ready de la Web Animations API (en-US) devuelve un Promise que se resuelve cuando la animación está lista para reproducirse. Una nueva 'promesa' es creada cada vez que la animación entra en play state(estado de reproducción) \"pending\"(pendiente) así como si la reproducción es cancelada, ya que en ambos escenarios, la animación estará lista para ser reiniciada.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Animation.ready","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"}],"source":{"folder":"es/web/api/animation/ready","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/es/web/api/animation/ready/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/es/docs/Web","title":"Tecnología para desarrolladores web"},{"uri":"/es/docs/Web/API","title":"Referencia de la API Web"},{"uri":"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation","title":"Animation"},{"uri":"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/ready","title":"Animation.ready"}],"pageTitle":"Animation.ready - Referencia de la API Web | MDN","noIndexing":false}}